latestPosts.caption:
A Birthday to Remember at Narendra Bhawan, Bikaner

Celebrating my birthday at Narendra Bhawan was truly unforgettable. This former royal residence of Maharaja Narendra Singhji is not just a hotel it’s a beautifully curated experience that blends history, luxury, and soul.

From the moment we arrived, the staff made us feel incredibly special. They were some of the kindest people we’ve ever met thoughtful, attentive, and genuinely warm. For my birthday, they went above and beyond: decorating our room, planning a surprise dinner under the stars, and making every moment feel personal and meaningful.

We also had one of the best spa experiences ever peaceful, luxurious, and deeply relaxing. It felt like a complete reset for the mind and body.

And let’s not forget the food every meal was full of flavor and love. From traditional Rajasthani dishes to creative, modern plates, each bite was memorable.

A special shoutout to our tourist guide, who was simply the best knowledgeable, kind, and passionate about Bikaner’s rich history. He made exploring the city even more meaningful and fun.

Narendra Bhawan gave us memories we’ll cherish forever. I couldn’t have asked for a more beautiful way to celebrate and I truly can’t wait to return.😮‍💨🫠🫠💌🥹 @narendra.bhawan.bikaner
